                                        "body": "In flood hazard areas as established in <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/colorado/irc-2021/chapter/3/building-planning#table_R301.2\">Table R301.2</a>, <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/colorado/irc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#combustion_air_\">combustion air</a></span> openings shall be located at or above the elevation required in <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/colorado/irc-2021/chapter/3/building-planning#R322.2.1\">Section R322.2.1</a> or <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/colorado/irc-2021/chapter/3/building-planning#R322.3.2\">R322.3.2</a>.",
